Class ConceptScraper

Object
ConceptScraper
Direct Known Subclasses:
ShopScraper, StockScraper
public abstract class ConceptScraper
extends Object
ConceptScraper is a abstract class to let the predefined classes use the methods from Scraper with correct inheriting.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Mathias Jarbekk, Thomas Johannessen, Joakim Jensen, Michal Kowalski
